<span style="font-family:Centaur; color:#e6d3a3; text-shadow: 0 0 20px #cfa43a">'''''"The human eye is designed to see only what is in front of him. It is not designed to see what lies behind him, nor is it meant to see beyond its own line of vision."'''</span>


