<span style="font-family:Centaur; color:#e6d3a3; text-shadow: 0 0 20px #cfa43a">'''''"Even if we could see the future. we would know what it lies for us. It is still possible that will be our future, but since we now know, it is possible to deviate from it."'''</span>


